.\" manpage for simple-shell. Simple shell project to Holberton School.
.\" Contact AUTHORS to correct errors or typos.
.TH simple_shell 0 "8 April 2022" "1.0" "simple-shell man page"

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hsh
[command]

.SH DESCRIPTION
This program is a simple shell


.SH INITIALIZATION
To use the ghost shell the user needs to compile using: gcc.

.SH The command for compiler:
gcc -Wall -Wextra -Werror -pedantic *.c -o hsh

.B hsh
is a shell command for executes commands.


.SH EXAMPLES
.B 1. Non interactice mode example:
$ echo "/bin/ls" | ./hsh
hsh main.c shell.c test_ls_2
$
$ cat test_ls_2
/bin/ls
/bin/ls
$
$ cat test_ls_2 | ./hsh
hsh main.c shell.c test_ls_2
hsh main.c shell.c test_ls_2
$

.B 2. Interactice mode example:
$ ./hsh
($) /bin/ls
hsh main.c shell.c
($)
($) exit
$

.SH BUILT-IN COMMANDS
.B env
- prints environ Variables
.B exit
- exits the hell

.SH BUGS
No known bugs.

.SH RETURN
shell basic

